---
import BlogLayout from '../layouts/BlogLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
---

<BlogLayout title="About - M1NDB3ND3R" description="Learn more about M1NDB3ND3R, a computer science student's blog exploring algorithms, programming, and technology.">
  <Header />
  
  <main class="main">
    <div class="container">
      <article class="about-content">
        <header class="about-header">
          <h1 class="about-title">About M1NDB3ND3R</h1>
          <p class="about-subtitle">
            A computer science student's journey through the digital realm
          </p>
        </header>
        
        <section class="about-body">
          <div class="intro-section">
            <h2>Hello, World!</h2>
            <p>
              Welcome to my corner of the internet. I'm a computer science student passionate about 
              algorithms, programming languages, and the endless possibilities of technology. 
              This blog serves as my digital notebook where I share insights, document my learning 
              process, and explore complex concepts.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="mission-section">
            <h2>The Mission</h2>
            <p>
              My goal is simple: make complex computer science concepts accessible without 
              sacrificing technical depth. Whether you're a fellow student, a seasoned developer, 
              or just curious about how computers work, I hope you find something valuable here.
            </p>
            
            <div class="values-grid">
              <div class="value-card">
                <h3>Learning</h3>
                <p>Every post is an opportunity to dive deeper into a topic and share what I discover.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="value-card">
                <h3>Clarity</h3>
                <p>Complex ideas deserve clear explanations. I strive to make difficult concepts understandable.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="value-card">
                <h3>Curiosity</h3>
                <p>The best learning happens when we ask questions and explore beyond the surface.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="topics-section">
            <h2>What I Write About</h2>
            <div class="topics-grid">
              <div class="topic-item">
                <h3>Algorithms & Data Structures</h3>
                <p>Deep dives into fundamental CS concepts, complexity analysis, and implementation strategies.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="topic-item">
                <h3>Programming Languages</h3>
                <p>Exploring different languages, their strengths, and unique approaches to problem-solving.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="topic-item">
                <h3>Software Engineering</h3>
                <p>Best practices, design patterns, and lessons learned from building real-world applications.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="topic-item">
                <h3>Computer Theory</h3>
                <p>Mathematical foundations, computational theory, and the principles that power modern computing.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="philosophy-section">
            <h2>My Philosophy</h2>
            <blockquote>
              "The best way to learn is to teach, and the best way to understand is to implement."
            </blockquote>
            <p>
              I believe that true understanding comes from getting your hands dirty with code, 
              working through problems, and sharing knowledge with others. This blog is my 
              contribution to the amazing community of developers and learners who make 
              the tech world such an exciting place.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="contact-section">
            <h2>Let's Connect</h2>
            <p>
              I love connecting with fellow developers, students, and anyone interested in 
              computer science. Feel free to reach out if you have questions, suggestions, 
              or just want to discuss an interesting problem.
            </p>
            <div class="contact-info">
              <p>
                <strong>Email:</strong> radhikatharun02@gmail.com<br>
                <strong>GitHub:</strong> @tharun-dv<br>
                <strong>Twitter:</strong> @mindbender08
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
      </article>
    </div>
  </main>
</BlogLayout>

<style>
  .main {
    min-height: 100vh;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1rem;
  }

  .about-content {
    padding: 2rem 0 4rem;
  }

  .about-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #333;
    padding-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .about-title {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .about-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: #ccc;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .about-body {
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .about-body h2 {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  .about-body p {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: #ccc;
  }

  .intro-section {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .mission-section {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .values-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .value-card {
    background-color: #1a1a1a;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    border: 1px solid #333;
  }

  .value-card h3 {
    color: #ffffff;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .value-card p {
    color: #ccc;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .topics-section {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .topics-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .topic-item {
    background-color: #1a1a1a;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    border: 1px solid #333;
  }

  .topic-item h3 {
    color: #ffffff;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .topic-item p {
    color: #ccc;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .philosophy-section {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .philosophy-section blockquote {
    margin: 2rem 0;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background-color: #1a1a1a;
    border-left: 4px solid #ffffff;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  .contact-section {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .contact-info {
    background-color: #1a1a1a;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    border: 1px solid #333;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .contact-info p {
    margin-bottom: 0;
    font-family: 'Fira Code', monospace;
  }

  .contact-info strong {
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-title {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .about-subtitle {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    .about-body h2 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    .values-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .topics-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
</BlogLayout>